channel.title: Astrect - Development Team
channel.description:
[img]http://i.imgur.com/Pvool.png[/img] [b]Introduction:[/b] Welcome to Astrect's development thread. Astrect will be a server based on economy. It would be a semi-remake of my previous project called: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=514816.0]Vertigo[/url] Which should now go even farther. We already have a Vps and domain.
[b]Team:[/b]
[ul][li]Ryley Kimmel - [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=516337]AtomicInt_[/url] - Server developer[/li] [li]Artem Batutin - [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=454285]artem543[/url] - Client developer[/li] [li]Empty - Server developer [ Who can build custom contents (Minigames, Quests,Skills)[/li] [li]Empty - Client developer[/li][/ul]
[b]Application:[/b] [code] Can you code Java: Position: Experience (Scale 1-10): Age: Time you will use a day on the server: Have you had this position in another server: MSN: Skype: [/code]
[b]Goals:[/b]
[ul][li]Unique Customs areas[/li] [li]Great stability[/li] [li]New data / old data?[/li] [li]Unique features[/li] [li]Unique Mini-games[/li] [li]Great server base [+100][/li] [li]PvP Action[/li] [li]Allot of quests[/li][/ul]
